---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pago de Permiso - Policía Nacional del Perú" bodyClass="no-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Inicio</a>
      <span><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
      <a href="/dni"><i class="fas fa-id-card"></i> DNI</a>
      <span><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
      <a href="/licencia"><i class="fas fa-car"></i> Licencia</a>
      <span><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
      <a href="/registro-vehicular"><i class="fas fa-car-side"></i> Vehículo</a>
      <span><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
      <a href="/soat"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> SOAT</a>
      <span><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
      <span>Pago</span>
    </nav>

    <!-- Auth Prompt (hidden if logged in) -->
    <div id="pago-auth-required" class="info-box" style="display: none; background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1); border-color: var(--error-color);">
      <h3 style="color: var(--error-color); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Inicio de Sesión Requerido</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Para asociar tu pago de forma oficial, debes iniciar sesión con tu cuenta PNP.</p>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary" style="display: inline-flex; width: auto; padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;">Iniciar Sesión</a>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
      <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
      <p>Este pago es necesario para procesar su registro y otorgarle el permiso de lunas polarizadas.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="monto-box">
      <h2>Monto a pagar</h2>
      <div class="monto">S/. 120.00</div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-card" id="pago-form-card">
      <form id="formPago">
        <h3 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--accent-green);">
          <i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i> Método de Pago
        </h3>

        <div class="metodo-pago">
          <input type="radio" id="tarjeta" name="metodo" value="tarjeta" checked>
          <label for="tarjeta">
            <i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i>
            <span>Tarjeta</span>
          </label>

          <input type="radio" id="banco" name="metodo" value="banco">
          <label for="banco">
            <i class="fas fa-university"></i>
            <span>Banco</span>
          </label>

          <input type="radio" id="yape" name="metodo" value="yape">
          <label for="yape">
            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
            <span>Yape</span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <!-- TARJETA -->
        <div id="formTarjeta" class="section-pago active">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="bancoTarjeta">Banco Emisor</label>
            <select id="bancoTarjeta" name="banco" class="form-control" required>
              <option value="" disabled selected>Seleccione su banco</option>
              <option value="BBVA">BBVA</option>
              <option value="Interbank">Interbank</option>
              <option value="BCP">BCP</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="numeroTarjeta">Número de Tarjeta</label>
            <input type="password" name="tarjeta" id="numeroTarjeta" class="form-control"
                   minlength="16" maxlength="16" placeholder="0000 0000 0000 0000" required>
          </div>

          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem;">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="cvc">CVC</label>
              <input type="password" name="cvc" id="cvc" class="form-control"
                     minlength="3" maxlength="4" placeholder="000" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="mesAnio">Vencimiento</label>
              <input type="month" name="mesAnio" id="mesAnio" class="form-control" required>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="codigo-pago" id="codigoPagoTarjeta" style="display: none;">
            <p><i class="fas fa-barcode"></i> <strong>Código de Pago Generado</strong></p>
            <div class="codigo" id="tarjetaGenCode">ABC12345</div>
            <p>Copie este código y péguelo abajo para validar su pago.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- BANCO -->
        <div id="formBanco" class="section-pago" style="display: none;">
          <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            Seleccione su banco para realizar la transferencia
          </p>
          <div class="bancos">
            <img src="https://gestion.pe/resizer/8x2AlIgYkCU3SG-UJ2-HozYZKCc=/1200x583/smart/filters:format(jpeg):quality(75)/arc-anglerfish-arc2-prod-elcomercio.s3.amazonaws.com/public/YHZXKA5EN5CCNO3IYKOSJARW7M.jpg" 
                 data-banco="BBVA" alt="BBVA">
            <img src="https://images.seeklogo.com/logo-png/28/1/interbank-2015-logo-png_seeklogo-285084.png" 
                 data-banco="Interbank" alt="Interbank">
            <img src="https://www.logotypes101.com/logos/611/B437AB14955AB7689AD24FC300E95928/bcp__logo_2014.png" 
                 data-banco="BCP" alt="BCP">
          </div>
          <input type="hidden" id="selectBanco" name="banco" />

          <div class="codigo-pago" id="codigoPagoBanco" style="display: none;">
            <p><i class="fas fa-university"></i> <strong>Datos para Transferencia</strong></p>
            <div class="codigo" id="bancoGenCode">ABC12345</div>
            <p>Realice su pago en la banca en línea de <strong id="bancoTransferLabel"></strong> usando este código.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- YAPE -->
        <div id="formYape" class="section-pago" style="display: none;">
          <div class="qr-section" style="text-align: center;">
            <p style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
              Escanee el código QR con su aplicación Yape
            </p>
            <img src="/JS/imagenes/yape.jpg" alt="Código QR Yape" style="max-width: 180px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 0 auto; display: block;" />
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <i class="fas fa-building"></i> <strong>Banco de la Nación</strong>
            </p>
            
            <div class="codigo-pago" id="codigoPagoYape" style="display: none; margin-top: 1rem;">
              <p><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> <strong>Código de Pago</strong></p>
              <div class="codigo" id="yapeGenCode">ABC12345</div>
              <p>Después de pagar, ingrese este código para validar su transacción.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
          <a href="/soat" class="btn btn-secondary" style="flex: 1;">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Volver
          </a>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="btnGenerarCodigo" style="flex: 2;">
            Generar Código de Pago
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>

      <!-- VALIDACIÓN -->
      <div class="validacion-form" id="validacionFormCard" style="display: none; margin-top: 2rem; border-top: 2px solid var(--border-color); padding-top: 2rem;">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Validar Pago</h3>
        <form id="formValidarPago">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="codigoIngresado">Ingrese el código de pago</label>
            <input type="text" id="codigoIngresado" class="form-control" maxlength="8" placeholder="ABC12345" required style="text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px;" />
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="btnValidarCodigo">
            <i class="fas fa-check"></i> Validar Código
          </button>
          <div class="alert-error" id="validationErrorAlert" style="display: none;">Código de pago inválido. Por favor intente de nuevo.</div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- PAGO VALIDADO -->
      <div class="alert-success" id="pagoExitosoCard" style="display: none; margin-top: 2rem; border: 1px solid var(--success-color);">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> ¡Pago Validado Correctamente!</h3>
        <p style="margin: 1rem 0; line-height: 1.6;">
          Gracias por completar su pago. Su solicitud ha sido registrada de manera exitosa. 
          <br><br>
          <strong>El trámite se encuentra actualmente en estado: <span style="color: var(--accent-yellow);">EN PROCESO</span>. Puede hacerle seguimiento en la sección del menú.</strong>
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; text-align: center;">
          <a href="/mis-tramites" class="btn btn-primary" style="display: inline-flex; width: auto; padding: 0.75rem 2rem;">
            <i class="fas fa-tasks"></i> Ir a Mis Trámites
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    import { supabase } from '../lib/supabase/client';

    const authPrompt = document.getElementById('pago-auth-required');
    const formCard = document.getElementById('pago-form-card');
    const formPago = document.getElementById('formPago') as HTMLFormElement;
    const formValidar = document.getElementById('formValidarPago') as HTMLFormElement;

    const formTarjeta = document.getElementById('formTarjeta');
    const formBanco = document.getElementById('formBanco');
    const formYape = document.getElementById('formYape');

    const selectBanco = document.getElementById('selectBanco') as HTMLInputElement;
    const validationFormCard = document.getElementById('validacionFormCard');
    const validationErrorAlert = document.getElementById('validationErrorAlert');
    const pagoExitosoCard = document.getElementById('pagoExitosoCard');

    let currentUserId: string | null = null;
    let currentGeneratedCode = '';

    // Auth and protection check
    window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', async () => {
      const { data: { session } } = await supabase.auth.getSession();
      
      if (!session) {
        if (authPrompt) authPrompt.style.display = 'block';
        // Disable inputs
        formPago.querySelectorAll('input, button, select').forEach(el => {
          (el as any).disabled = true;
        });
        return;
      }

      currentUserId = session.user.id;
    });

    // Handle Payment Options Toggles
    const radios = document.querySelectorAll('input[name="metodo"]');
    radios.forEach(radio => {
      radio.addEventListener('change', (e) => {
        const val = (e.target as HTMLInputElement).value;
        
        if (formTarjeta) formTarjeta.style.display = val === 'tarjeta' ? 'block' : 'none';
        if (formBanco) formBanco.style.display = val === 'banco' ? 'block' : 'none';
        if (formYape) formYape.style.display = val === 'yape' ? 'block' : 'none';

        // Clear code displays
        document.getElementById('codigoPagoTarjeta')!.style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('codigoPagoBanco')!.style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('codigoPagoYape')!.style.display = 'none';
        if (validationFormCard) validationFormCard.style.display = 'none';
        currentGeneratedCode = '';

        // Update requirements
        const cardNum = document.getElementById('numeroTarjeta') as HTMLInputElement;
        const cardCvc = document.getElementById('cvc') as HTMLInputElement;
        const cardDate = document.getElementById('mesAnio') as HTMLInputElement;
        const bankSelect = document.getElementById('bancoTarjeta') as HTMLSelectElement;

        if (val === 'tarjeta') {
          cardNum.required = true;
          cardCvc.required = true;
          cardDate.required = true;
          bankSelect.required = true;
        } else {
          cardNum.required = false;
          cardCvc.required = false;
          cardDate.required = false;
          bankSelect.required = false;
        }
      });
    });

    // Handle bank transfer logos click selection
    document.querySelectorAll('.bancos img').forEach(img => {
      img.addEventListener('click', () => {
        document.querySelectorAll('.bancos img').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('selected'));
        img.classList.add('selected');
        
        const bankName = img.getAttribute('data-banco') || '';
        selectBanco.value = bankName;

        // Auto trigger generation code on logo click
        generatePaymentCode();
      });
    });

    // Generate validation code action
    formPago?.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      generatePaymentCode();
    });

    const generatePaymentCode = () => {
      const activeMethod = (formPago.querySelector('input[name="metodo"]:checked') as HTMLInputElement).value;
      
      if (activeMethod === 'banco' && !selectBanco.value) {
        alert('Por favor seleccione su banco emisor.');
        return;
      }

      // Generate validation code
      const chars = 'ABCDEFGHJKLMNPQRSTUVWXYZ23456789';
      let code = '';
      for (let i = 0; i < 8; i++) {
        code += chars.charAt(Math.floor(Math.random() * chars.length));
      }
      currentGeneratedCode = code;

      // Render code depending on method
      if (activeMethod === 'tarjeta') {
        document.getElementById('tarjetaGenCode')!.textContent = code;
        document.getElementById('codigoPagoTarjeta')!.style.display = 'block';
      } else if (activeMethod === 'banco') {
        document.getElementById('bancoGenCode')!.textContent = code;
        document.getElementById('bancoTransferLabel')!.textContent = selectBanco.value;
        document.getElementById('codigoPagoBanco')!.style.display = 'block';
      } else if (activeMethod === 'yape') {
        document.getElementById('yapeGenCode')!.textContent = code;
        document.getElementById('codigoPagoYape')!.style.display = 'block';
      }

      // Show validator form
      if (validationFormCard) {
        validationFormCard.style.display = 'block';
        validationFormCard.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
      }
    };

    // Validar validation form submit
    formValidar?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();

      const typed = (document.getElementById('codigoIngresado') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim().toUpperCase();

      if (typed !== currentGeneratedCode) {
        if (validationErrorAlert) validationErrorAlert.style.display = 'block';
        return;
      }

      if (validationErrorAlert) validationErrorAlert.style.display = 'none';

      // Validation success! Write permission request to database
      try {
        const dni = sessionStorage.getItem('dni_tramite');
        const nombreCompleto = sessionStorage.getItem('nombre_tramite');
        const placa = sessionStorage.getItem('placa_tramite');
        const soatId = sessionStorage.getItem('soat_id_tramite');

        if (!dni || !placa || !currentUserId) {
          throw new Error('Información de trámite incompleta. Reinicie el proceso.');
        }

        const payload = {
          dni,
          nombre_completo: nombreCompleto,
          placa_vehiculo: placa,
          licencia_valida: true,
          soat_vigente: true,
          estado: 'EN_PROCESO',
          usuario_id: currentUserId,
          soat_id: soatId ? parseInt(soatId) : null,
          fecha_solicitud: new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0]
        };

        const { error } = await supabase
          .from('permisos_lunas_polarizadas')
          .insert(payload);

        if (error) {
          throw new Error(error.message);
        }

        // Show success card and hide payment forms
        formPago.style.display = 'none';
        if (validationFormCard) validationFormCard.style.display = 'none';
        if (pagoExitosoCard) pagoExitosoCard.style.display = 'block';

        // Clear session
        sessionStorage.removeItem('dni_tramite');
        sessionStorage.removeItem('nombre_tramite');
        sessionStorage.removeItem('placa_tramite');
        sessionStorage.removeItem('soat_id_tramite');
        sessionStorage.removeItem('modelo_vehiculo');
        sessionStorage.removeItem('color_vehiculo');

      } catch (err: any) {
        alert(`Error al registrar el trámite: ${err.message}`);
      }
    });

    // Theme toggler
    function toggleTheme() {
      const html = document.documentElement;
      const currentTheme = html.getAttribute('data-theme');
      const newTheme = currentTheme === 'dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
      html.setAttribute('data-theme', newTheme);
      localStorage.setItem('theme', newTheme);
      document.getElementById('themeIcon')!.className = newTheme === 'dark' ? 'fas fa-sun' : 'fas fa-moon';
    }
  </script>

  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .breadcrumb {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    .breadcrumb a {
      color: var(--accent-green);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .breadcrumb a:hover {
      color: #218838;
    }

    .form-card {
      background-color: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .form-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .form-header .icon {
      width: 70px;
      height: 70px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-green), #218838);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3);
    }

    .form-header .icon i {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: white;
    }

    .form-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .form-header p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .form-group label .required {
      color: var(--error-color);
      margin-left: 0.25rem;
    }

    .input-icon {
      position: relative;
    }

    .input-icon i {
      position: absolute;
      left: 1rem;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .form-control {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.875rem 1rem 0.875rem 3rem;
      border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .form-control:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--accent-green);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1);
    }

    .error-message {
      color: var(--error-color);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      display: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .success-message {
      color: var(--success-color);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      display: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .alert {
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      animation: slideIn 0.4s ease;
    }

    @keyframes slideIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
    }

    .alert-error {
      background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid var(--error-color);
      color: var(--error-color);
    }

    .alert-success {
      background: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid var(--success-color);
      color: var(--success-color);
    }

    .info-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1), rgba(33, 136, 56, 0.05));
      border: 1px solid var(--accent-green);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .info-box h3 {
      color: var(--accent-green);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .info-box ul {
      margin-left: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .form-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent-green);
      color: white;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #218838;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--border-color);
    }

    /* ===== PAYMENT SPECIFIC STYLES ===== */
    .monto-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-dark), #143520);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .monto-box .monto {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent-yellow);
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .metodo-pago {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .metodo-card {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .metodo-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent-green);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .metodo-card.active {
      border-color: var(--accent-green);
      background: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.05);
    }

    .metodo-card i {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .metodo-card.active i {
      color: var(--accent-green);
    }

    .metodo-card h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .section-pago {
      display: none;
      animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease;
    }

    .section-pago.active {
      display: block;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }

    .bancos {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
